{
  "stem": "9091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] and that's maybe-- maybe one of the reasons why he got killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was also because of that, because he was involved in politics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was afraid when the Germans were to come in, they'll-- he'll be on the list, and they will execute him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father had three brothers, and they all worked, since they were all poor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they had a relative-- I think it was an uncle of theirs-- that had a bakery, a big bakery in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they came of age-- so they one after the other went into that bakery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they worked there, and that's how they make the living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] wasn't educated, again, because of the conditions that she had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after they-- they married at a young age, and my mother went to work as well, and my father was working, and--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of factory, and I don't even know if it was the same factory where she worked [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She kept on changing positions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know really that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know that she was working all her years since young-- since she was very young, and she was helping and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and supporting the family.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We weren't religious, I said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but I don't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't recall really [INAUDIBLE]-- all this ended anyways when I was only six.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't recall any lack of-- I'll say we were well fed and dressed, and that's it, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we lived in a small apartment, nothing great.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I saw the apartment just-- I remembered everything about that apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I still remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
